HEADWORD: Sultanate
<hw>Sul"tan*ate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>sultanat</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The rule or dominion of a
sultan; sultanship.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The territory ruled by a sultan.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> soldanrie.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sultaness</ent>⟦br⟧
